org.apache.hadoop.resourceestimator.common.api

Class ResourceSkyline

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.resourceestimator.common.api.ResourceSkyline

  • public class ResourceSkyline
extends Object
    ResourceSkyline records the job identification information as well as job's requested containers information during its lifespan.
